CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 22, 1973, pg. 28, reads: "Allderdice Running Right Into Successful Season...Maybe - Discuss Team Strategy - Allderdice High Dragons front seven discuss basketball with Coach Jim Dunlap. Front is John West, Dunlap, and Eddie Coleman.  Standing are Mark Pennix Jr., Tom Jacoby, Ray Lowe, Chuck Hefflin and Dave Horovitz.  Missing is Kenny Bolds. (Harris Photo).
TitMainTitle: Allderdice High School basketball players, squatting from left: John West, Coach Jim Dunlap, Eddie Coleman; standing: Mark Pennix Jr., Tom Jacoby, Ray Lowe, Chuck Hefflin, and Dave Horovitz, posed in gymnasium
